d2a2207026a816e5d21428d1baa43a","tid":1753891,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"一定要將僆儂牆保存落嚟"},{"pid":"d1808bcf4b046ae20e4c92c85cf89a08d0263820","tid":1753891,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"86e352ed1447a341b3a8faa3e9ffb4ab6ec476a2","tid":1753891,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"&mdash; 聘請手足做議員助理(我個區條仆街工賊以前淨請自己老婆仔女做助理，每個人每月月薪兩皮幾)<br />\n&mdash; 社區美化計劃，連儂牆/隧道/天橋合法化，物資由區議會提供<br />\n&mdash; 各區區議會合辦二手賣物會，俾人擺攤賣家中&quot;唔要&quot;嘅嘢(如$1賣豬嘴眼罩頭盔)<br />\n&mdash;  辦事處&quot;寄賣&quot;，&quot;寄賣&quot;屋企冇位放/會俾藍絲父母丟嘅嘢<br />\n&mdash; 不限年齡&quot;蛇齋餅粽&quot;唔使淨係靠唔知供應到幾耐嘅飯卷"},{"pid":"f16c930cbaa123f1b334c493dd95275378e362ac","tid":1753891,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5aab381b7b00bc0853a6a9e30f60033fb1ffceb","tid":1753891,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"值得諗諗<br />\n但係咪區議員權力範圍內?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"一個區議員就係自己區<br />\n一班區議員就講緊全個選區(如大埔區黃大仙區)<br />\n<br />\n買埋物資俾文宣組都仲